title.rendered: Spacefold Folding Round Outdoor Poseur Table

content.rendered:
The Spacefold Round Outdoor Poseur Table is part of our new deluxe range of folding tables. The Folding bases are made from aluminium meaning they are perfect for both indoor and outdoor use.

Featuring our new Extreme High Pressure Laminate Table Tops suitable for use both indoors and outdoors. These tops are weatherproof, highly scratch resistant and UV resistant. Made from sustainable resources.

The tops come with a 1 year warranty.

This item is held in stock for delivery in 3 working days.

Some basic self-assembly is required.

Fixing kit is included, Screws excluded.
